# Generic model-binary exclusion. The Phase 3 artifacts (pca.joblib, rf.joblib)
# are explicitly committed (Q7 confirmed: each ~10 KB, well under the 5 MB
# budget v3 §4.1/§4.2 sets); the rules below catch any future *large*
# model output that would bloat the repo.
models/*.pkl
models/*.h5
# Larger joblib variants get excluded; the Phase 3 .joblib pair are
# explicitly allow-listed below.
models/*-large.joblib
!models/pca.joblib
!models/rf.joblib
